org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.objectinspector.primitive

Class PrimitiveObjectInspectorUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.objectinspector.primitive.PrimitiveObjectInspectorUtils

  • public final class PrimitiveObjectInspectorUtils
extends Object
    ObjectInspectorFactory is the primary way to create new ObjectInspector instances. SerDe classes should call the static functions in this library to create an ObjectInspector to return to the caller of SerDe2.getObjectInspector().

        public static PrimitiveObjectInspectorUtils.PrimitiveGrouping getPrimitiveGrouping(PrimitiveObjectInspector.PrimitiveCategory primitiveCategory)
        Based on the PrimitiveCategory of a type, return the PrimitiveGrouping that the PrimitiveCategory belongs to (numeric, string, date, etc).
        Parameters:
        primitiveCategory - Primitive category of the type
